<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body { background-color: #ffffff; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; color: #333333; margin: 0; padding: 0;
      } .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;
      text-align: center; border: 2px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 8px; } .logo
      { max-width: 200px; margin-bottom: 15px; } .title { color: #404040;
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; margin-bottom:
      20px; } .divider { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; height: 2px;
      background: #e5e5e5; } .content { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .support { font-size: 14px; color: #999999; margin-top: 20px; } .link {
      color: #fff; font-weight: bold; background-color: #0077B5; margin: 0 auto;
      text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 25px; max-width: 500px; height: 50px;
      border-radius: 5px;} .link-title {color: #fff; font-weight: bold;} .name {
      color: #404040; } .support { font-size: 14px; color: #999999; margin-top:
      20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="http://localhost:3000">
        <img class="logo" src="cid:icon" />
      </a>
      <div class="title">{{title}}</div>
      <div class="divider" />
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <b class="name">{{name}}</b>,</p>
        {{!-- <p>To complete your resetting password for
          <span class="em">{{name}}</span>, please use the following OTP
          (One-Time Password) code:</p> --}}
        {{!-- <h2 class="link">{{code}}</h2> --}}
        <p>To ensure this function is not misused by unauthorised third parties,
          we will only replace your password once you have called up the
          following link in your browser:
        </p>
        {{! <p class="link" hr> }}
        <a href={{url}} class="link">
          <span class="link-title">Reset Password</span>
        </a>
        {{! </p> }}
        {{! <p>
          This OTP code is valid for 5 minutes. Make sure to change the password
          within these minutes, otherwise you will have to generate another link
          to enable the change of your password.
        </p> }}
        <p>This link is valid for 3 minutes. After you have clicked on the above
          link, you will be able to set a new password. Make sure you do not
          share your personal login information with others.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="support">
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to reach
        out to us at
        <a href="mailto:grooveit96@gmail.com">grooveit96@gmail.com</a>. We are
        here to help!
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>